oggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 03, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104aqj1665702893427.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aqj1665702893427.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/aqj1665702893427.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"aqj1665702893427\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Java Call-In Exceptions\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"aqj1665702893427__java_call_in_exceptions_115747\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Errors detected by Java methods are signaled by throwing exceptions.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3632e1_d3633e1_d3634e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Uniface Exceptions</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3632e1_d3633e1_d3634e1__entry__1\">\n Exception\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3632e1_d3633e1_d3634e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3632e1_d3633e1_d3634e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">NoSuchComponentException</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3632e1_d3633e1_d3634e1__entry__2\">\n Thrown when designated component does not exist or could not be created.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3632e1_d3633e1_d3634e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">NoSuchOperationException</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3632e1_d3633e1_d3634e1__entry__2\">\n Thrown when the designated component has no operation with the given name.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3632e1_d3633e1_d3634e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UnifaceException</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3632e1_d3633e1_d3634e1__entry__2\">\n Thrown for all error messages, except the two above. The text of the exception includes the Uniface error code.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"aqj1665702893427__p_d35912e1_d35913e1_d35914e1\">These exceptions are thrown at specific levels of the Java program. These levels are shown in the table:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3635e1_d3636e1_d3637e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Levels Where Exceptions are Thrown</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3635e1_d3636e1_d3637e1__entry__1\">\n Level\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3635e1_d3636e1_d3637e1__entry__2\">\n Exceptions thrown\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3635e1_d3636e1_d3637e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">constructor</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3635e1_d3636e1_d3637e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">NoSuchComponentException</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">UnifaceException</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3635e1_d3636e1_d3637e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">activate</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3635e1_d3636e1_d3637e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">NoSuchOperationException</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">UnifaceException</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3635e1_d3636e1_d3637e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">remove</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">accept</code>, <code class=\"ph codeph\">exec</code>,\n                        <code class=\"ph codeph\">quit</code>, and all user-defined methods. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"aqj1665702893427__table_d3635e1_d3636e1_d3637e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">UnifaceException</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525832\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525832\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Java Call-In Exceptions Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 03, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Java Call-In Exceptions Errors detected by Java methods are signaled by throwing exceptions. Table 1. Uniface Exceptions Exception Meaning NoSuchComponentException Thrown when designated component does not exist or could not be created. NoSuchOperationException Thrown when the designated component has no operation with the given name. UnifaceException Thrown for all error messages, except the two above. The text of the exception includes the Uniface error code. These exceptions are thrown at specific levels of the Java program. These levels are shown in the table: Table 2. Levels Where Exceptions are Thrown Level Exceptions thrown constructor NoSuchComponentException and UnifaceException activate NoSuchOperationException and UnifaceException remove , accept , exec , quit , and all user-defined methods. UnifaceException Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}